gnd_control.model

Interface VehicleStateListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GND_Control, Interractive_GUI, MyGoogleMap, VehicleStatus

    public interface VehicleStateListener
    VehicleStateListener interface defines an interface for all classes who wish to monitor the status of a vehicle.

    • Method Summary
